Test Case 2: Battery Level Display Accuracy

Test Case ID: TC-02
Title: Verify battery level is displayed correctly in the app


Preconditions:
Device is paired and in an active Bluetooth connection state with the app
Device has measurable battery level (>10%)


Test Steps:
1.Open the app.
2.Ensure the device is connected.
3.Check the displayed battery level in the app.
4.Compare it with the actual device battery level.
5.Reduce device battery (e.g., by continuous audio streaming) to simulate battery level change.
6.Observe updated battery level in the app.


Expected Result:
App displays battery level matching the device within acceptable tolerance.
Battery updates are reflected correctly after change.
No delay or incorrect values are shown in the UI.
